今天是一号吗?; jin1tian1 shi4 yi1hao4 ma?; Is today the first (of the month)?
昨天是一号，今天是二号。;zuo2tian1 shi4 yi1hao4, jin1tian1 shi4 er4 hao4.; Yesterday was the first, today is the second.
今天是二号吗？;jin1tian1 shi4 er4hao4 ma?; Is today the second?
你今天去北京吗？我今天不去北京;Ni3 jin1tian1 qu4 Bei3jing1 ma? Wo3 jin1tian1 bu2 qu4 Bei3jing1; Are you going to Beijing today? I am not going to Beijing today.
我三号去北京。;Wo3 san1hao4 qu4 Bei3jing1.; I am going to Beijing on the third.
我今天不去北京。;Wo3 jin1tian1 bu2 qu4 Bei3jing1.; I am not going to Beijing today.
你五号回吗？不，我四号回。;Ni3 wu3hao4 hui2 ma? Bu4 wo3 si4hao4 hui2.; Are you coming back on the fifth? No, I will be back on the fourth.
你今天去广州吗？我今天去，五号回。;Ni3 jin1tian1 qu4 guang3zhou1 ma? Wo3 jin1tian1 qu4, wu3hao4 hui2.; Are you going to Guangzhou today? Yes, I am going today and come back on the fifth.
他们是四个美国人。;ta1men shi4 ge mei3guo2ren2.; They are 4 Americans.
我四号回美国人。;wo3 si4hao4 hui2 mei3guo2.; I return to America on the 4th.
我有三个弟弟。;wo3 you3 san1 ge di4di; I have 3 younger brothers.
他明天回美国。;ta1 ming2tian1 hui2 mei3guo2.; He will go back to America tomorrow.
你去那里？我去北京。;ni3 qu4 na3li? wo3 qu4 bei3jing1.; Where did you go? I went to Beijing.
小明是一个好学生。;Xiao3ming2 shi4 yi2ge hao3 xue2shen1; Xiao Ming is a good student.
